      <title>随着降息速度放缓，福林引领新兴货币上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/forint-leads-emerging-currency-gains-as-rate-cuts-seen-slowing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期匈牙利央行将在当天晚些时候放慢降息步伐，福林在新兴市场货币中领涨，而美元回调则小幅提振了 MSCI 的广泛新兴市场货币指标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/forint-leads-emerging-currency-gains-as-rate-cuts-seen-slowing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 10:35:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可可飙升至 10,000 美元破纪录，重创巧克力制造商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/cocoa-soars-past-10-000-pummeling-chocolate-and-candy-makers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可可期货飙升至每吨前所未有的 10,000 美元以上，延续了今年价格翻倍的历史性上涨趋势，并导致巧克力成本上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/cocoa-soars-past-10-000-pummeling-chocolate-and-candy-makers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 10:19:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行行长曼表示，市场定价今年英国降息次数过多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/boe-s-mann-says-markets-pricing-too-many-uk-rate-cuts-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行政策制定者凯瑟琳·曼表示，金融市场已经消化了今年过多的降息，英国不太可能先于美联储采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/boe-s-mann-says-markets-pricing-too-many-uk-rate-cuts-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 09:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
